'''Conflict-Red''' was a stage of [[New Republic Defense Force/Legends|New Republic Defense Force]] military status.

It was raised only when combat was about to begin or was already underway. Other stages of military status included [[Conflict-Orange]] and [[Conflict-Yellow]].

